cts of being stunned or confused. The player cannot control the direction of their actions. The player also loses control of teleports and polymorphs.\"/>\n<link rel=\"image_src\" href=\"/images/6/65/Nethackwiki-logo.png\"/>\n<link rel=\"shortcut icon\" href=\"/images/6/64/Favicon.ico\"/>\n<link rel=\"search\" type=\"application/opensearchdescription+xml\" href=\"/opensearch_desc.php\" title=\"NetHackWiki\"/>\n<link rel=\"EditURI\" type=\"application/rsd+xml\" href=\"https://nethackwiki.com/api.php?action=rsd\"/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"/wiki/Afraid\"/>\n<!--[if lt IE 9]><script src=\"/load.php?debug=false&amp;lang=en&amp;modules=html5shiv&amp;only=scripts&amp;skin=vector&amp;sync=1\"></script><![endif]-->\n</head>\n<body class=\"mediawiki ltr sitedir-ltr mw-hide-empty-elt ns-0 ns-subject page-Afraid rootpage-Afraid skin-vector action-view\">\t\t<div id=\"mw-page-base\" class=\"noprint\"></div>\n\t\t<div id=\"mw-head-base\" class=\"noprint\"></div>\n\t\t<div id=\"content\" class=\"mw-body\" role=\"main\">\n\t\t\t<a id=\"top\"></a>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"mw-indicators mw-body-content\">\n</div>\n<h1 id=\"firstHeading\" class=\"firstHeading\" lang=\"en\">Afraid</h1>\t\t\t<div id=\"bodyContent\" class=\"mw-body-content\">\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"siteSub\" class=\"noprint\">From NetHackWiki</div>\t\t\t\t<div id=\"contentSub\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"jump-to-nav\"></div>\t\t\t\t<a class=\"mw-jump-link\" href=\"#mw-head\">Jump to navigation</a>\n\t\t\t\t<a class=\"mw-jump-link\" href=\"#p-search\">Jump to search</a>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"mw-content-text\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\" class=\"mw-content-ltr\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><dl><dd><span class=\"dablink\"><i>For monsters being scared of the player, see <a href=\"/wiki/Scare\" title=\"Scare\">Scare</a>.</i></span></dd></dl>\n<p>In <a href=\"/wiki/SpliceHack\" title=\"SpliceHack\">SpliceHack</a>, the player can sometimes become too <b>afraid</b> to control their actions.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Effects\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Effects</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Causes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Causes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Prevention\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Prevention</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Cures\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Cures</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Strategy\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Strategy</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Effects\">Effects</span></h2>\n<p>The effects of being afraid are similar to the effects of being <a href=\"/wiki/Stunned\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Stunned\">stunned</a> or <a href=\"/wiki/Confused\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Confused\">confused</a>. The player cannot control the direction of their actions. The player also loses control of teleports and polymorphs.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Causes\">Causes</span></h2>\n<ul><li>the roar of a <a href=\"/wiki/Dragon\" title=\"Dragon\">dragon</a>, including <a href=\"/wiki/Dragon_(SpliceHack)\" title=\"Dragon (SpliceHack)\">SpliceHack-specific dragons</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>the <a href=\"/wiki/Gaze\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Gaze\">gaze</a> of a <a href=\"/index.php?title=Bodak&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Bodak (page does not exist)\">bodak</a> or <a href=\"/index.php?title=Eye_of_fear_and_flame&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Eye of fear and flame (page does not exist)\">eye of fear and flame</a></li>\n<li>the scream of a <a href=\"/index.php?title=Banshee&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Banshee (page does not exist)\">banshee</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Prevention\">Prevention</span></h2>\n<p>Fear-inducing gaze attacks can be avoided by being <a href=\"/wiki/Blind\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Blind\">blind</a>. Becoming blind after becoming afraid does not remove the fear, however.\n</p><p>A dragon's roar will not scare a player who is <i>both</i> blind and <a href=\"/wiki/Deaf\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Deaf\">deaf</a>. There is also a random chance of resisting becoming afraid of a roar.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Cures\">Cures</span></h2>\n<ul><li>waiting for the effect to time out</li>\n<li>drinking <a href=\"/wiki/Potion_of_booze\" title=\"Potion of booze\">booze</a> (\"liquid courage\")</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Strategy\">Strategy</span></h2>\n<p>Players should save all the booze they can in case they become afraid. In particular, blessed booze can dispel the afraid effect without also causing confusion. There are many guaranteed potions of booze at the <a href=\"/wiki/Bar_(SpliceHack)\" title=\"Bar (SpliceHack)\">Bar</a>: pick them up and keep them safe.\n</p><p>A more drastic measure is to annihilate (<a href=\"/wiki/Genocide\" title=\"Genocide\">genocide</a>) all dragons: the other sources of fear are rarer and easier to deal with. However there are severe downsides to doing so: dragons drop valuable <a href=\"/wiki/Corpse\" title=\"Corpse\">corpses</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/Dragon_scales\" title=\"Dragon scales\">dragon scales</a> when they die. Additionally dragons can be good <a href=\"/wiki/Pet\" title=\"Pet\">pets</a>. Annihilating dragons is probably only worth it to players pursuing the teetotal (no alcohol) <a href=\"/wiki/Unofficial_conduct\" title=\"Unofficial conduct\">unofficial conduct</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span></h2>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"external free\" href=\"https://github.com/NullCGT/SpliceHack/blob/b29334720e353ee991bba3e657d22bacbe78a523/src/mon.c#L3854-L3874\">https://github.com/NullCGT/SpliceHack/blob/b29334720e353ee991bba3e657d22bacbe78a523/src/mon.c#L3854-L3874</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20240926182221\nCache expiry: 604800\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.011 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.036 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 77/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 607/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 125/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 61/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 6/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 529/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   16.327      1 -total\n 43.00%    7.021      1 Template:Of\n 28.17%    4.600      1 Template:For\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key wikihackdb:pcache:idhash:37939-0!canonical and timestamp 20240926182221 and revision id 146020\n -->\n</div></div>\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"printfooter\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tRetrieved from \"<a dir=\"ltr\" href=\"https://nethackwiki.com/index.php?title=Afraid&amp;oldid=146020\">https://nethackwiki.com/index.php?title=Afraid&amp;oldid=146020</a>\"\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"catlinks\" class=\"catlinks\" data-mw=\"interface\"><div id=\"mw-normal-catlinks\" clas